content.name: Remove Fog: The Teladi Outpost
content.description: Fog in Fields of Opportunity [FO] becomes invisible. Should improve FPS.
content.author: Vectorial1024

text.name: 去去雾气走：The Teladi Outpost
text.description: [FO]的雾气不再可见。应可提升帧率(FPS)。

text.name: 去去霧霾走：The Teladi Outpost
text.description: [FO]的霧氣不再可見。應可提升幀率(FPS)。
